<view class="edit-page">
  <view class="edit-header" style="padding-top: {{statusHeight}}px">
    <view class="header-left" bindtap="goBack">
      <t-icon name="chevron-left" size="48rpx" />
    </view>
    <view class="header-title">{{id ? '编辑提醒' : '新增提醒'}}</view>
    <view class="header-right"></view>
  </view>

  <view class="form">
    <view class="field">
      <view class="label">规则名称</view>
      <t-input value="{{form.name}}" placeholder="未填写时自动生成" data-field="name" bind:change="onInput" />
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <view class="label">提醒方向</view>
      <t-radio-group value="{{form.direction}}" bind:change="onDirectionChange">
        <t-radio wx:for="{{directionOptions}}" wx:key="value" value="{{item.value}}">{{item.label}}</t-radio>
      </t-radio-group>
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <view class="label">目标价格</view>
      <t-input
        value="{{form.target_price}}"
        type="digit"
        placeholder="请输入目标价格"
        data-field="target_price"
        bind:change="onInput"
      />
    </view>


    <view class="field">
      <view class="label">冷却时间（分钟）</view>
      <t-input
        value="{{form.cooldown_minutes}}"
        type="number"
        placeholder="默认 720"
        data-field="cooldown_minutes"
        bind:change="onInput"
      />
      <view class="hint cooldown-hint">
        同一条提醒触发后，在这段时间内不会重复记录。默认 720 分钟即 12 小时，可减少频繁打扰。
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="switch-row">
      <view>
        <view class="label">启用提醒</view>
        <view class="hint">关闭后不会写入新的触发记录</view>
      </view>
      <t-switch value="{{form.enabled}}" bind:change="onEnabledChange" />
    </view>

    <t-button block theme="primary" size="large" bindtap="onSubmit">保存提醒</t-button>
    <view class="notice">本服务仅提供黄金价格信息与提醒功能，不构成投资建议。</view>
  </view>
</view>
